physicalDescription.note: Typed on sticker on back of photograph: ''Jewish Historical Society; of the Upper Midwest; Hamline U., 1536 Hewitt Av.; St. Paul, MN 55104.'' Handwritten on back of photograph: ''#1017, JCNS Branch, 1916; Poale Zion.''

mods.abstract: A group of unidentified men and women sit and stand in a field in front of a tree. The men in front hold a sign with the year 1916 written on it along with several Hebrew phrases and two stars of David.
